<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
<title>添加系统管理员</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"
	href="<%=request.getContextPath()%>/css/table.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"
